	<h1 class="title">「这世界」迈阿密的博物馆发生了流血事件，结果都没人当真</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4695/small/4695.jpg?1418026962" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙若空 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-07 13:07:29 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18614/medium/18614.jpg?1449464503" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


